(a + b)^n = \sum_{i=0}^{n}  a^ib^{n-i}\binom{n}{i}
1.04^2 = (1 + 0.04)^2 = 1^0\times0.04^2 \binom{2}{0} + 1^1\times0.04^1 \binom{2}{1} + 1^2\times0.04^0 \binom{2}{2} = 1.0816
